---
import Steps from "@xtyle/astro/Steps.astro";
import Card from "@xtyle/astro/Card.astro";
import Heading from "@xtyle/astro/Heading.astro";
import Stack from "@xtyle/astro/Stack.astro";
import Badge from "@xtyle/astro/Badge.astro";
import Text from "@xtyle/astro/Text.astro";
---

<Stack gap={6}>
	<Card>
		<Heading slot="header" level={3} size="sm">Checkout</Heading>
		<Steps current={1}>
			<ol>
				<li>Cart</li>
				<li>Shipping</li>
				<li>Payment</li>
				<li>Review</li>
			</ol>
		</Steps>
	</Card>

	<Card>
		<Heading slot="header" level={3} size="sm">Nearly done</Heading>
		<Steps current={3}>
			<ol>
				<li>Account</li>
				<li>Profile</li>
				<li>Preferences</li>
				<li>Confirm</li>
			</ol>
		</Steps>
	</Card>

	<Card>
		<Heading slot="header" level={3} size="sm">Nothing done yet</Heading>
		<Steps current={0}>
			<ol>
				<li id="step-brief">Brief</li>
				<li id="step-draft">Draft</li>
				<li id="step-review">Review</li>
			</ol>
		</Steps>
	</Card>

	<Card>
		<Heading slot="header" level={3} size="sm">Steps with real content</Heading>
		<Steps current={2}>
			<ol>
				<li><strong>Upload</strong> <Badge tone="success" size="sm">done</Badge></li>
				<li><strong>Transcode</strong> <Badge tone="success" size="sm">done</Badge></li>
				<li><strong>Publish</strong> <Badge tone="accent" size="sm">now</Badge></li>
			</ol>
		</Steps>
	</Card>

	<Card>
		<Heading slot="header" level={3} size="sm">Zero-JS</Heading>
		<Stack gap={4}>
			<Text size="sm" tone="muted">
				The Astro binding splits the authored <code>&lt;li&gt;</code>s against <code>current</code> on the server, so the
				markers, the connectors, and the done / current / upcoming states are all resolved at build time.
				<code>static</code> keeps it that way: the stepper below never asks for the runtime and stays a complete, fully-styled
				indicator with zero JavaScript. Reacting to a changed <code>current</code> is what hydration adds on top.
			</Text>
			<Steps static current={2}>
				<ol>
					<li>Authored</li>
					<li>Rendered</li>
					<li>Shipped</li>
					<li>Hydrated</li>
				</ol>
			</Steps>
		</Stack>
	</Card>
</Stack>
